WEBVTT

1
00:00:08.091 --> 00:00:10.093
[unsettling music playing]

2
00:00:17.684 --> 00:00:19.227
[Saeng-gang] Tell me. Crown Prince.

3
00:00:21.021 --> 00:00:22.814
Why do you resent Father?

4
00:00:26.735 --> 00:00:28.445
Why are you doing this?

5
00:00:29.446 --> 00:00:32.115
Now you mean to hurt Father
after murdering Prince Yeongan?

6
00:00:32.615 --> 00:00:33.700
[Crown Prince] Look closely.

7
00:00:34.868 --> 00:00:37.412
[Saeng-gang breathes nervously]

8
00:00:37.495 --> 00:00:38.913
[Crown Prince] Look closely.

9
00:00:40.749 --> 00:00:42.000
See how I died.

10
00:00:53.094 --> 00:00:54.846
-[gasps]
-[music intensifies]

11
00:00:54.929 --> 00:00:57.265
[Crown Prince]
It was Father who poisoned me.

12
00:00:58.391 --> 00:01:00.393
[sizzling]

13
00:01:04.022 --> 00:01:06.149
Father killed me.

14
00:01:07.859 --> 00:01:09.611
-Now you know.
-[gasps]

15
00:01:10.153 --> 00:01:11.946
[gasps] You're awake!

16
00:01:12.030 --> 00:01:13.031
Your Majesty.

17
00:01:13.114 --> 00:01:14.240
[Chief Eunuch] Your Majesty.

18
00:01:15.867 --> 00:01:16.743
[King groans]

19
00:01:20.288 --> 00:01:21.122
Chief Eunuch.

20
00:01:21.206 --> 00:01:22.499
Yes. Your Majesty.

21
00:01:22.582 --> 00:01:24.709
Summon the Chief Royal Secretary.

22
00:01:25.210 --> 00:01:27.170
[sinister music playing]

23
00:01:27.253 --> 00:01:28.171
[Sukbin] Your Majesty.

24
00:01:30.965 --> 00:01:32.801
[King] We have no time to spare.

25
00:01:35.011 --> 00:01:37.555
The plague must be contained at once.

26
00:01:37.639 --> 00:01:39.432
Carry out the edict as written.

27
00:01:43.228 --> 00:01:46.731
[splutters] Are you saying
that you are ordering us to kill

28
00:01:46.815 --> 00:01:48.858
everyone in the entire village.
Your Majesty?

29
00:01:48.942 --> 00:01:51.277
PUT THEM ALL TO DEATH

30
00:01:53.530 --> 00:01:55.156
And do not delay.

31
00:01:56.449 --> 00:01:58.076
[Crown Prince] <i>He is an ak-gwi.</i>

32
00:02:00.036 --> 00:02:02.288
A living. breathing ak-gwi.

33
00:02:03.748 --> 00:02:05.750
It was Father who killed me.

34
00:02:07.418 --> 00:02:10.672
He killed me
when I learned of all of his sins.

35
00:02:11.631 --> 00:02:13.633
[dramatic percussive music playing]

36
00:02:15.218 --> 00:02:17.220
[sizzling]

37
00:02:18.721 --> 00:02:22.600
[Crown Prince] And now you will be next
since you know the secret as well.

38
00:02:23.434 --> 00:02:25.103
-I am next.
-He will kill you too.

39
00:02:25.186 --> 00:02:27.397
You are next.
You know the secret. do you not?

40
00:02:27.480 --> 00:02:29.774
Father poisoned me.
Father killed me. He killed all of us.

41
00:02:29.858 --> 00:02:31.651
I will die next.

42
00:02:31.734 --> 00:02:33.444
[Crown Prince] He will kill you soon.

43
00:02:33.945 --> 00:02:35.947
I know the truth as well.

44
00:02:36.030 --> 00:02:38.158
[music swells]

45
00:02:39.117 --> 00:02:42.871
THE EAST PALACE

46
00:02:42.954 --> 00:02:44.706
[Crown Prince] <i>You are next.</i>

47
00:02:44.789 --> 00:02:46.624
[music fades]

48
00:02:46.708 --> 00:02:48.710
[Gu-cheon breathing heavily]

49
00:02:52.380 --> 00:02:54.841
[grunts. pants]

50
00:03:01.806 --> 00:03:02.974
Damn it.

51
00:03:04.475 --> 00:03:06.519
I can't see clearly from here either.

52
00:03:07.020 --> 00:03:09.564
[pants]

53
00:03:09.647 --> 00:03:11.774
[unsettling ethereal music playing]

54
00:03:11.858 --> 00:03:14.277
[footsteps pattering]

55
00:03:50.980 --> 00:03:52.440
[Gu-cheon] Princess.

56
00:03:54.359 --> 00:03:55.860
[footsteps approaching]

57
00:03:57.779 --> 00:03:59.781
[ominous music playing]

58
00:04:07.330 --> 00:04:10.541
[King] You defied my direct order
to save Prince Yeongan.

59
00:04:11.042 --> 00:04:14.295
And in spite of that.
you hid in here and deceived me.

60
00:04:15.546 --> 00:04:17.507
making your King look like a fool.

61
00:04:17.590 --> 00:04:20.927
And because of that. Your Majesty.
I saved you from the spirit.

62
00:04:21.010 --> 00:04:23.179
I'm told you unearthed
the Crown Prince. Is that right?

63
00:04:23.805 --> 00:04:24.973
Where is the body now?

64
00:04:25.556 --> 00:04:27.308
I'm unable to tell you that.

65
00:04:27.809 --> 00:04:31.020
It is essential to destroy the spirit.

66
00:04:31.104 --> 00:04:34.565
Even if that spirit
was your son. Your Majesty.

67
00:04:39.404 --> 00:04:41.322
I will give you ten days.

68
00:04:41.406 --> 00:04:43.157
Destroy the spirit within that time.

69
00:04:43.241 --> 00:04:44.284
But ten will not suffice.

70
00:04:44.367 --> 00:04:45.451
Ten days.

71
00:04:45.535 --> 00:04:49.080
If so. then you must follow
every one of my instructions.

72
00:04:49.163 --> 00:04:50.957
[Chief Eunuch] Mind your tongue.
How dare you speak to His--

73
00:04:51.040 --> 00:04:53.918
[Gu-cheon] I will place a protective ward
in your bedchamber

74
00:04:54.002 --> 00:04:56.296
to keep the spirit from entering the room.

75
00:04:56.379 --> 00:04:58.840
Unless you wish to cough up more blood

76
00:05:00.091 --> 00:05:02.260
and linger before death's door.

77
00:05:15.189 --> 00:05:16.607
On one condition.

78
00:05:17.108 --> 00:05:18.151
And that is

79
00:05:19.527 --> 00:05:21.904
it's to be installed outside the hall.

80
00:05:43.593 --> 00:05:44.677
[breathes heavily]

81
00:05:44.761 --> 00:05:46.512
[music fades]

82
00:05:52.769 --> 00:05:54.771
[dark music playing]

83
00:05:56.439 --> 00:05:57.315
There you are.

84
00:05:57.398 --> 00:05:59.067
[pressing music playing]

85
00:05:59.150 --> 00:06:00.151
[Gu-cheon] Princess.

86
00:06:02.528 --> 00:06:03.571
Princess.

87
00:06:03.654 --> 00:06:04.697
Saeng-gang!

88
00:06:07.408 --> 00:06:08.659
It can't beâ€¦

89
00:06:12.705 --> 00:06:14.957
Princess. are you all right?

90
00:06:17.752 --> 00:06:19.754
[pressing music continues]

91
00:06:23.758 --> 00:06:25.676
[gasps]

92
00:06:25.760 --> 00:06:27.428
[music fades]

93
00:06:27.512 --> 00:06:28.679
[Gu-cheon] Are you all right?

94
00:06:35.812 --> 00:06:37.563
[sighs] What happened?

95
00:06:38.481 --> 00:06:40.066
You lost consciousness.

96
00:06:42.026 --> 00:06:45.988
It appears thatâ€¦ you were
taken over by the Crown Prince.

97
00:06:47.949 --> 00:06:50.743
He decided to use your body
to hide his own.

98
00:06:52.829 --> 00:06:53.955
Then he mustâ€¦

99
00:06:54.914 --> 00:06:56.707
He must still be clinging on to me?

100
00:06:57.291 --> 00:06:58.334
I don't know.

101
00:06:59.961 --> 00:07:01.170
You don't know?

102
00:07:03.840 --> 00:07:07.009
I can't see any spirits.
I injured my eyes in the Realm of Gwi.

103
00:07:09.887 --> 00:07:11.431
Get some rest for now.

104
00:07:12.515 --> 00:07:14.684
I will go look for
the Crown Prince's body.

105
00:07:16.227 --> 00:07:17.395
That will not be necessary.

106
00:07:20.022 --> 00:07:21.482
What do you mean by that?

107
00:07:22.108 --> 00:07:24.569
Even if you do find his body
and put his spirit to rest.

108
00:07:24.652 --> 00:07:27.447
it has been made clear
that we will not be spared.

109
00:07:29.198 --> 00:07:31.200
For it is the King
that killed his own son.

110
00:07:34.704 --> 00:07:35.997
Killed his own son?

111
00:07:36.080 --> 00:07:38.082
[mysterious ethereal music playing]

112
00:07:40.960 --> 00:07:44.338
[Saeng-gang] <i>The rice they had placed</i>
<i>in his mouth had turned black.</i>

113
00:07:46.674 --> 00:07:48.217
He was poisoned.

114
00:07:53.598 --> 00:07:55.725
If we do not meet a similar fate.

115
00:07:57.268 --> 00:08:00.062
then we must uncover the incidents
and find the proof

116
00:08:00.146 --> 00:08:01.731
of what happened 30 years ago.

117
00:08:01.814 --> 00:08:03.024
That it was all my father.

118
00:08:04.150 --> 00:08:07.111
We must do this
before more people are killed.

119
00:08:07.987 --> 00:08:10.615
[man] I sent the troops and carried out
the order you commanded.

120
00:08:10.698 --> 00:08:13.451
However. some soldiers decided
they should release

121
00:08:13.534 --> 00:08:17.330
several women and children.
and those who did appear to have fled.

122
00:08:23.753 --> 00:08:27.381
And are those who took it upon themselves
to release them still there?

123
00:08:28.341 --> 00:08:30.301
They are. Your Majesty.

124
00:08:30.384 --> 00:08:31.802
-Seize them all.
-[paper rustles]

125
00:08:31.886 --> 00:08:34.138
[King] Then.
in front of the rest of the troopsâ€¦

126
00:08:36.682 --> 00:08:37.975
behead each one.

127
00:08:42.271 --> 00:08:43.773
[music fades]

128
00:08:45.441 --> 00:08:49.320
I suppose that I have no choice
but to meet the Crown Prince's spirit.

129
00:08:50.404 --> 00:08:51.906
What do you mean by that?

130
00:08:51.989 --> 00:08:54.534
I must ask directly how he learnedâ€¦

131
00:08:55.076 --> 00:08:56.702
learned of the crimes my father committed.

132
00:08:57.828 --> 00:08:59.789
He might be asking for my help

133
00:09:00.414 --> 00:09:02.625
so that he may ease his resentment.

134
00:09:02.708 --> 00:09:06.671
Princess. he's an ak-gwi
who has taken lives.

135
00:09:07.380 --> 00:09:08.673
So forget it.

136
00:09:09.340 --> 00:09:10.424
Here. make this instead.

137
00:09:14.095 --> 00:09:15.805
What am I looking at?

138
00:09:15.888 --> 00:09:18.975
A ward to keep
the Crown Prince's spirit from clinging.

139
00:09:19.058 --> 00:09:20.810
Itâ€™s best to keep it attached to you.

140
00:09:26.148 --> 00:09:27.191
[Saeng-gang sighs]

141
00:09:27.275 --> 00:09:29.277
[poignant string music playing]

142
00:09:30.194 --> 00:09:32.321
[paper rustling]

143
00:09:38.244 --> 00:09:39.954
It must be frustrating

144
00:09:40.955 --> 00:09:42.498
not being able to see anymore.

145
00:09:44.709 --> 00:09:46.460
There's one good thing though.

146
00:09:47.878 --> 00:09:50.506
It's nice that.
for the first time in my life.

147
00:09:51.299 --> 00:09:53.843
I can't see spirits or gwi-maes at all.

148
00:10:00.391 --> 00:10:02.018
Then you'd wish to

149
00:10:03.644 --> 00:10:05.730
continue not being able to see?

150
00:10:07.648 --> 00:10:08.774
Forever?

151
00:10:11.611 --> 00:10:13.446
Whatever my wishes are.

152
00:10:14.488 --> 00:10:17.491
my sight must return
if we want to find the Crown Prince.

153
00:10:19.035 --> 00:10:20.953
It's the only way we'll get through this.

154
00:10:44.268 --> 00:10:46.312
What are you doing?

155
00:10:48.439 --> 00:10:50.775
I just wanted to check whether

156
00:10:50.858 --> 00:10:53.152
the Crown Prince's spirit
has secretly clung to you.

157
00:10:55.071 --> 00:10:59.283
But with my sight as it is.
how could I even know. right?

158
00:11:09.168 --> 00:11:10.836
About your eyesightâ€¦

159
00:11:10.920 --> 00:11:12.296
[music fades]

160
00:11:13.297 --> 00:11:16.342
Do you think it is restorable?

161
00:11:16.425 --> 00:11:19.387
I have to find
the damn shaman who did this to me.

162
00:11:21.263 --> 00:11:24.058
The one hiding him is the one wishing
for the King to be dead.

163
00:11:24.141 --> 00:11:26.143
[intriguing music playing]

164
00:11:27.561 --> 00:11:29.438
Do you suspect anyone at all?

165
00:11:35.152 --> 00:11:37.738
[music swells. fades]

166
00:11:37.822 --> 00:11:40.533
Why have you come all the way here?

167
00:11:41.033 --> 00:11:42.827
[Saeng-gang] I have a matter
to inquire about.

168
00:11:42.910 --> 00:11:45.246
Have you held a shamanic rite lately?

169
00:11:45.329 --> 00:11:47.123
[Queen] A shamanic rite?

170
00:11:47.707 --> 00:11:50.000
When Prince Yeongan collapsed.
I believe it was you

171
00:11:50.084 --> 00:11:51.627
who summoned a shaman.

172
00:11:51.711 --> 00:11:53.254
Where might he be currently?

173
00:11:53.337 --> 00:11:57.049
You sought me out to ask such a thing?
You wretched child.

174
00:11:57.633 --> 00:12:00.803
After everything you did.
you have the nerve.

175
00:12:00.886 --> 00:12:01.762
[seethes]

176
00:12:01.846 --> 00:12:04.974
You've become pathetic.

177
00:12:05.474 --> 00:12:06.559
[grunts]

178
00:12:07.226 --> 00:12:09.437
-Your Majesty.
-[Queen coughs]

179
00:12:13.107 --> 00:12:15.359
[slurps. coughs]

180
00:12:15.443 --> 00:12:18.529
[Queen exhales. slurps]

181
00:12:20.865 --> 00:12:22.533
What's important isâ€¦

182
00:12:26.662 --> 00:12:28.622
I would guess that he has to be

183
00:12:28.706 --> 00:12:31.792
the feng shui master
His Majesty brought in.

184
00:12:31.876 --> 00:12:33.878
Why have you arrived with him?

185
00:12:33.961 --> 00:12:37.089
He's inspecting the palace grounds
by His Majesty's command.

186
00:12:37.173 --> 00:12:39.842
-The Queen Dowager's--
-You speak nothing but lies.

187
00:12:39.925 --> 00:12:44.430
[sniffles] I know full well
of the heinous acts he has done here.

188
00:12:46.307 --> 00:12:48.893
You. speak for yourself.

189
00:12:48.976 --> 00:12:52.605
Is there still a spirit in this palace

190
00:12:52.688 --> 00:12:54.982
that wants to end
the royal bloodline or not?

191
00:12:55.065 --> 00:12:58.194
A spirit in the palace? Uncle would scoff
and simply laugh in your presence.

192
00:12:58.277 --> 00:13:00.279
[screams] What did you say?

193
00:13:01.614 --> 00:13:03.574
Whether spirits are at work or not.

194
00:13:03.657 --> 00:13:06.994
is it not a relief
that His Majesty has recovered?

195
00:13:07.578 --> 00:13:10.247
Considering that the plague
continues to spread.

196
00:13:10.331 --> 00:13:13.501
Oh. Princess. have you not heard yet?

197
00:13:13.584 --> 00:13:15.085
Your Father

198
00:13:15.836 --> 00:13:18.297
deployed his troops
to where the plague had broken out.

199
00:13:18.380 --> 00:13:19.882
and once thereâ€¦

200
00:13:22.802 --> 00:13:24.762
commanded that everyone be put to death.

201
00:13:24.845 --> 00:13:27.014
-[ominous music playing]
-[breathes shakily]

202
00:13:31.894 --> 00:13:35.272
[Iksang] Children and elders alike.
every last one of them. dead.

203
00:13:35.356 --> 00:13:37.358
[people screaming]

204
00:13:37.441 --> 00:13:39.443
[child breathing heavily]

205
00:13:46.283 --> 00:13:48.828
[Crown Prince] <i>He is an ak-gwi.</i>
<i>A living. breathing ak-gwi.</i>

206
00:13:48.911 --> 00:13:51.247
<i>He is an ak-gwi.</i>
<i>A living. breathing ak-gwi.</i>

207
00:13:52.248 --> 00:13:53.290
[woman screams]

208
00:13:53.374 --> 00:13:57.753
[Iksang] <i>They say it was the first act</i>
<i>His Majesty took upon awakening.</i>

209
00:13:57.837 --> 00:13:59.213
-[people screaming]
-[sobs]

210
00:13:59.296 --> 00:14:01.549
-Mother!
-[guard] Leave no one alive!

211
00:14:01.632 --> 00:14:03.217
[panicked screaming]

212
00:14:03.300 --> 00:14:06.512
[child] Mother! Please. wake up.

213
00:14:08.264 --> 00:14:09.807
[Crown Prince] <i>He will kill everyone.</i>

214
00:14:09.890 --> 00:14:11.141
<i>Father poisoned me.</i>

215
00:14:11.225 --> 00:14:12.893
<i>He will put us all to death.</i>

216
00:14:12.977 --> 00:14:15.437
<i>You are next. He will kill you soon.</i>

217
00:14:15.521 --> 00:14:16.522
<i>He is an ak-gwi.</i>

218
00:14:16.605 --> 00:14:17.565
[gasps]

219
00:14:20.317 --> 00:14:22.778
Get your hands off the Princess at once.

220
00:14:24.405 --> 00:14:25.573
[breathes shakily]

221
00:14:26.490 --> 00:14:29.076
A centipede
as large as a snake was on you.

222
00:14:30.119 --> 00:14:31.912
What's with all the bugs here?

223
00:14:36.250 --> 00:14:38.210
[Saeng-gang] Uncle. what news do you have
for Her Highness?

224
00:14:38.294 --> 00:14:40.045
Have you come
to report on the plague matter?

225
00:14:40.129 --> 00:14:41.463
I have no official post.

226
00:14:41.547 --> 00:14:43.966
Why would I concern myself
with matters such as this?

227
00:14:44.049 --> 00:14:46.343
The reason I have an audience
with Her Royal Highness

228
00:14:46.427 --> 00:14:49.346
is to pay my respects.
as His Majesty issued an edict

229
00:14:49.430 --> 00:14:51.932
appointing my eldest son

230
00:14:53.809 --> 00:14:55.728
as Crown Prince.

231
00:14:56.228 --> 00:14:58.230
[unsettling music playing]

232
00:15:02.818 --> 00:15:07.031
[King] <i>Bring Prince Iksang's eldest son.</i>
<i>Prince Inha. into the palace</i>

233
00:15:07.114 --> 00:15:10.159
<i>so he can learn the proper customs</i>
<i>and hold the investiture ceremony</i>

234
00:15:10.242 --> 00:15:11.702
<i>as soon as possible.</i>

235
00:15:12.328 --> 00:15:14.204
<i>The nation is in turmoil.</i>

236
00:15:14.705 --> 00:15:17.791
<i>Since the East Palace</i>
<i>cannot remain vacant any longer.</i>

237
00:15:17.875 --> 00:15:21.003
<i>I will take Prince Inha as my adopted son</i>

238
00:15:21.086 --> 00:15:23.047
<i>and seat him upon the throne.</i>

239
00:15:25.382 --> 00:15:26.800
[Saeng-gang] <i>He will kill me.</i>

240
00:15:27.843 --> 00:15:29.178
<i>I know he will.</i>

241
00:15:30.179 --> 00:15:31.597
<i>He is a man</i>

242
00:15:32.723 --> 00:15:34.725
<i>who killed his own son.</i>

243
00:15:35.267 --> 00:15:38.604
<i>He would notâ€¦ hesitate.</i>

244
00:15:39.647 --> 00:15:43.025
RABBIT

245
00:15:43.734 --> 00:15:44.568
[grunts]

246
00:15:46.111 --> 00:15:47.404
[music fades]

247
00:15:47.988 --> 00:15:51.075
[sighs] Why? Why'd you hit me?

248
00:15:51.742 --> 00:15:53.202
You need to get a hold of yourself.

249
00:15:53.285 --> 00:15:56.330
Dark thoughts weaken your mind
and make the heart fall apart.

250
00:15:56.830 --> 00:15:59.375
A spirit could just slide in
through those cracks.

251
00:16:00.042 --> 00:16:00.918
[sighs]

252
00:16:01.627 --> 00:16:02.836
[Gu-cheon] Set the ward.

253
00:16:03.963 --> 00:16:06.632
My sight still fails me.
so you will have to do it.

254
00:16:14.682 --> 00:16:15.766
[Gu-cheon inhales sharply]

255
00:16:17.059 --> 00:16:18.060
Lower.

256
00:16:18.769 --> 00:16:20.729
-Place it lower.
-I'm doing that.

257
00:16:21.522 --> 00:16:23.023
It's as low as it can be.

258
00:16:23.565 --> 00:16:24.566
RABBIT

259
00:16:24.650 --> 00:16:25.484
I said to--

260
00:16:25.567 --> 00:16:27.820
I'm letting this slide
only because you can barely see.

261
00:16:31.949 --> 00:16:33.075
[Gu-cheon sighs]

262
00:16:36.787 --> 00:16:40.207
Why are we putting up these rabbit signs.
and why upside down?

263
00:16:40.290 --> 00:16:43.043
The Crown Prince was born
in the Year of the Rabbit.

264
00:16:43.627 --> 00:16:44.962
If it's upside down.

265
00:16:45.921 --> 00:16:49.466
his soul cannot pass through here
without a body to hide in.

266
00:16:51.760 --> 00:16:53.554
So you need to be careful.

267
00:16:54.263 --> 00:16:56.765
Unless you wish
to have your body taken by him.

268
00:16:57.266 --> 00:16:59.393
There was no other choice
when it happened.

269
00:17:01.478 --> 00:17:03.897
I'm not sure
how one could stay so collected

270
00:17:04.398 --> 00:17:06.525
after finding out
your father's a murderer.

271
00:17:07.276 --> 00:17:09.278
[gentle piano music playing]

272
00:17:10.738 --> 00:17:12.322
I'll say this again.

273
00:17:12.865 --> 00:17:15.576
You must keep your wits about you
going forward.

274
00:17:18.620 --> 00:17:20.956
If not.
you must stay close to somebody else.

275
00:17:21.040 --> 00:17:22.750
somebody you can rely on.

276
00:17:31.842 --> 00:17:35.012
There is someone
that I can rely on about this.

277
00:17:35.095 --> 00:17:37.097
[footsteps approaching]

278
00:17:44.271 --> 00:17:45.355
[Sukbin] Saeng-gang.

279
00:17:46.899 --> 00:17:48.192
Hello. Grandmother.

280
00:17:48.275 --> 00:17:49.693
[Sukbin] Have you been well?

281
00:17:51.612 --> 00:17:53.155
Good for her. I'm glad.

282
00:17:53.238 --> 00:17:55.365
-You are leaving the palace?
-[music fades]

283
00:17:55.908 --> 00:17:58.535
I came here
so I could tend to Prince Yeongan.

284
00:17:58.619 --> 00:18:01.330
But that's no longer possible.
unfortunately.

285
00:18:01.413 --> 00:18:02.706
With you and Gu-cheon here.

286
00:18:02.790 --> 00:18:05.125
His Majesty should be safe
from all of this.

287
00:18:05.751 --> 00:18:09.254
However. this matter
of the late Crown Princeâ€¦

288
00:18:10.130 --> 00:18:13.092
It's hard to believe
he's become a spirit. isn't it?

289
00:18:14.426 --> 00:18:15.427
[Sukbin sighs]

290
00:18:18.847 --> 00:18:23.018
This palace is truly
a frightening place to be.

291
00:18:23.560 --> 00:18:25.646
It's not a place for an old woman.

292
00:18:28.023 --> 00:18:30.025
[man tuts] He looks like a walking corpse.

293
00:18:30.109 --> 00:18:32.694
-[man 2] I hear you.
-[man] Right? He can't even eat or speak.

294
00:18:33.237 --> 00:18:35.322
If a shaman loses their presiding deity.

295
00:18:35.405 --> 00:18:36.824
they honestly may as well be dead.

296
00:18:36.907 --> 00:18:38.700
Heavens! Let's get going.

297
00:18:40.035 --> 00:18:43.330
[wheezing. snoring]

298
00:18:44.706 --> 00:18:46.583
[inhales]

299
00:18:46.667 --> 00:18:49.253
[labored breathing]

300
00:18:50.087 --> 00:18:52.089
[breathing shakily]

301
00:18:52.673 --> 00:18:54.675
[gasping]

302
00:18:56.552 --> 00:18:58.345
[ominous music swells]

303
00:18:59.930 --> 00:19:03.892
[spectral voices murmuring]

304
00:19:17.281 --> 00:19:19.283
[spectral voices murmuring]

305
00:19:26.123 --> 00:19:27.124
[groans]

306
00:19:32.880 --> 00:19:33.964
[music swells]

307
00:19:34.756 --> 00:19:38.135
[spectral screaming]

308
00:19:38.927 --> 00:19:40.429
-[loud thud]
-[Gu-cheon grunts]

309
00:19:40.929 --> 00:19:43.265
[groaning. grunts]

310
00:19:44.183 --> 00:19:46.935
[grunting. groaning]

311
00:19:47.019 --> 00:19:50.189
[pants. screams]

312
00:19:50.939 --> 00:19:52.941
[panting]

313
00:19:54.151 --> 00:19:56.153
[music intensifies]

314
00:19:59.990 --> 00:20:02.034
[spectral voices murmuring]

315
00:20:03.035 --> 00:20:04.661
[Crown Prince] Take me in.

316
00:20:04.745 --> 00:20:06.830
[whimpers]

317
00:20:06.914 --> 00:20:09.166
[panting]

318
00:20:12.002 --> 00:20:14.296
[groaning]

319
00:20:16.173 --> 00:20:17.132
[grunts]

320
00:20:17.216 --> 00:20:18.258
[groans]

321
00:20:27.392 --> 00:20:30.229
[Crown Prince]
I shall be your new presiding deity.

322
00:20:31.063 --> 00:20:34.358
[screams] Your Royal Highness!

323
00:20:42.032 --> 00:20:44.618
-[music fades]
-[Gu-cheon groaning]

324
00:20:47.788 --> 00:20:48.747
[door opens]

325
00:20:49.539 --> 00:20:50.582
[Gu-cheon pants]

326
00:20:50.666 --> 00:20:51.667
[door closes]

327
00:20:51.750 --> 00:20:53.126
[uneasy music playing]

328
00:20:56.463 --> 00:20:58.048
[Saeng-gang] Gu-cheon. what happened?

329
00:20:58.131 --> 00:20:59.258
[exhales sharply]

330
00:21:01.051 --> 00:21:02.177
[Gu-cheon] My eyes.

331
00:21:03.136 --> 00:21:05.013
I can't see at all anymore.

332
00:21:09.142 --> 00:21:10.602
That damned shaman.

333
00:21:11.645 --> 00:21:14.231
He must have burned the object
that cursed my eyes.

334
00:21:14.314 --> 00:21:16.692
He's already begun
with a new presiding deity.

335
00:21:22.739 --> 00:21:24.866
Isn't there something we can do about it?

336
00:21:25.575 --> 00:21:28.036
Now that I can't see spirits at all.

337
00:21:29.371 --> 00:21:31.206
this work is doomed.

338
00:21:33.208 --> 00:21:35.294
Is there any way
to bring back some of your sight?

339
00:21:40.340 --> 00:21:43.510
There is one way.
but it is far too dangerous.

340
00:21:44.803 --> 00:21:46.013
Why is that?

341
00:21:46.096 --> 00:21:49.182
Because it means disturbing
what must never be disturbed.

342
00:21:57.399 --> 00:21:59.609
But if you're able
to bring back your visionâ€¦

343
00:22:02.070 --> 00:22:03.196
then we must do it.

344
00:22:03.280 --> 00:22:04.114
No.

345
00:22:04.906 --> 00:22:07.909
I would rather flee
than commit such an act.

346
00:22:08.702 --> 00:22:11.330
I will survive somehow.
as long as I stay hidden.

347
00:22:12.664 --> 00:22:14.833
Where do you think you're going?
You can't see anymore!

348
00:22:19.254 --> 00:22:21.131
Since it's come to this.

349
00:22:21.715 --> 00:22:23.633
you should flee the palace
and come with me.

350
00:22:23.717 --> 00:22:27.054
The moment we flee. His Majesty will
send out his troops to have us beheaded.

351
00:22:27.888 --> 00:22:31.099
And I don't wish to leave the palace again
for something that was not my fault.

352
00:22:31.683 --> 00:22:32.809
like when I was a child.

353
00:22:34.227 --> 00:22:37.397
I will have to seek out the Crown Prince's
spirit alone if you won't help us.

354
00:22:37.481 --> 00:22:40.359
I'll find a way to keep us both safe.
even if you can't.

355
00:22:40.442 --> 00:22:42.110
And how would you do that alone?

356
00:22:43.653 --> 00:22:44.905
[intriguing music playing]

357
00:22:44.988 --> 00:22:47.199
[Saeng-gang] If the Crown Prince's spirit
comes near me.

358
00:22:48.533 --> 00:22:49.659
I'm not going to stop it.

359
00:22:50.494 --> 00:22:53.121
Do you not remember
how dangerous this is for you?

360
00:22:53.789 --> 00:22:54.998
If the spirit takes your body--

361
00:22:55.082 --> 00:22:55.999
That will not happen.

362
00:22:56.083 --> 00:23:00.629
No matter the cost.
His Majesty's sins must be proven.

363
00:23:06.968 --> 00:23:08.762
You have honestly gone insane.

364
00:23:19.856 --> 00:23:21.608
[music fades]

365
00:23:21.691 --> 00:23:25.070
Did you see the Princess's complexion?

366
00:23:25.570 --> 00:23:28.073
[Jang] Her complexion. Your Majesty?

367
00:23:30.617 --> 00:23:31.868
Did it not look as though

368
00:23:31.952 --> 00:23:35.831
she was being tormented
by a kind of spirit?

369
00:23:36.331 --> 00:23:40.335
So could that spirit. the Court Lady.

370
00:23:40.419 --> 00:23:42.546
still linger in the palace walls?

371
00:23:42.629 --> 00:23:43.880
Definitely not.

372
00:23:43.964 --> 00:23:46.007
That tragic young man called Gu-cheon

373
00:23:46.091 --> 00:23:48.844
certainly destroyed the spirit
of the Most Favored Lady.

374
00:23:48.927 --> 00:23:50.679
I felt my body grow lighter.

375
00:23:50.762 --> 00:23:54.391
All of the resentment
I had to endure has now vanished.

376
00:23:54.474 --> 00:23:56.726
And yet Prince Yeongan still died.

377
00:23:56.810 --> 00:24:00.397
and both His Majesty
and the Princess have fallen ill.

378
00:24:04.526 --> 00:24:10.240
Could it be that another vengeful spirit
is after the throne and His Majesty?

379
00:24:10.323 --> 00:24:12.325
[unsettling music playing]

380
00:24:13.076 --> 00:24:16.037
Oh. Yourâ€¦ Your Majesty.

381
00:24:16.121 --> 00:24:20.083
[Queen] It was my very own shame
that clouded my sight.

382
00:24:20.167 --> 00:24:23.295
Why was His Majesty
the only son of the late King

383
00:24:23.378 --> 00:24:26.047
to have somehow survived this calamity?

384
00:24:26.131 --> 00:24:30.302
How did he. out of everyone.
survive the terrible curse?

385
00:24:31.761 --> 00:24:35.182
-<i>Indeed. There must be another cause.</i>
-That will be all today. Your Highness.

386
00:24:35.265 --> 00:24:38.018
[Queen] <i>There was a physician</i>
<i>at the Royal Infirmary</i>

387
00:24:38.101 --> 00:24:41.396
<i>who examined the Princes</i>
<i>that died 30 years ago.</i>

388
00:24:41.480 --> 00:24:43.190
<i>Find him at once.</i>

389
00:24:49.571 --> 00:24:51.031
He is dead?

390
00:24:51.823 --> 00:24:53.366
[Jang] Yes. Your Majesty.

391
00:24:53.450 --> 00:24:57.954
I traced the royal physician who attended
to the Princes that died 30 years ago.

392
00:24:58.038 --> 00:25:00.540
And. a few years after that.

393
00:25:00.624 --> 00:25:03.585
he suddenly vomited dark blood and died.

394
00:25:03.668 --> 00:25:07.589
The symptoms seem to match those
of the dead Princes.

395
00:25:10.217 --> 00:25:14.012
So. whatever targeted the royal house

396
00:25:14.763 --> 00:25:17.182
was not the work of spirits here.

397
00:25:19.935 --> 00:25:20.852
[Jang] Pardon?

398
00:25:24.773 --> 00:25:27.692
Where is Prince Iksang's son right now?

399
00:25:31.863 --> 00:25:33.615
Oh! Prince Inha!

400
00:25:33.698 --> 00:25:35.200
-[woman] Madam!
-Prince. what happened?

401
00:25:35.283 --> 00:25:37.118
[gasps] No!

402
00:25:37.202 --> 00:25:38.495
Summon the physician at once.

403
00:25:38.578 --> 00:25:39.454
Yes!

404
00:25:40.205 --> 00:25:42.207
[breathing heavily]

405
00:25:47.587 --> 00:25:49.214
[music fades]

406
00:25:51.466 --> 00:25:53.009
What brings you here so late?

407
00:25:53.093 --> 00:25:55.720
You have been summoned
by Her Majesty. Princess.

408
00:25:56.304 --> 00:25:57.472
[Saeng-gang] For what reason?

409
00:25:58.223 --> 00:26:00.267
[Jang] Prince Inha has fallen unconscious.

410
00:26:02.561 --> 00:26:04.646
Then why is it I have been summoned?

411
00:26:05.313 --> 00:26:06.606
In his chamber.

412
00:26:07.440 --> 00:26:08.900
we found a box of confectioneries.

413
00:26:08.984 --> 00:26:10.277
[sighs] Mm.

414
00:26:10.944 --> 00:26:12.112
[unsettling music playing]

415
00:26:12.195 --> 00:26:15.532
[Jang] It bears the same markings
as the box you brought Her Royal Majesty

416
00:26:15.615 --> 00:26:16.783
the Queen Dowager.

417
00:26:16.866 --> 00:26:17.784
[breathes shakily]

418
00:26:17.867 --> 00:26:20.078
[Jang] Her Majesty says
that he appears to have collapsed

419
00:26:20.161 --> 00:26:22.789
after consuming what was inside the box.

420
00:26:28.712 --> 00:26:29.921
[muffled] Your Highness?

421
00:26:30.922 --> 00:26:33.174
[footsteps echo]

422
00:26:43.310 --> 00:26:44.436
[Sukbin muffled] Saeng-gang.

423
00:26:46.396 --> 00:26:47.439
Saeng-gang.

424
00:26:47.939 --> 00:26:49.357
-[clear] Saeng-gang!
-[gasps]

425
00:26:49.941 --> 00:26:50.942
[Sukbin] Saeng-gang.

426
00:26:51.026 --> 00:26:52.444
[music fades]

427
00:26:53.028 --> 00:26:55.530
What is wrong with you?
Have you come to your senses?

428
00:26:58.199 --> 00:26:59.576
Wait. why am I here?

429
00:26:59.659 --> 00:27:01.494
I'm wondering that as well.

430
00:27:01.578 --> 00:27:04.247
You appeared out of nowhere
and just stood there without a word.

431
00:27:04.331 --> 00:27:06.166
I should take my leave from here.

432
00:27:09.961 --> 00:27:13.256
What is going on with you?
You can tell me. your grandmother.

433
00:27:18.094 --> 00:27:19.220
Grandmother.

434
00:27:21.222 --> 00:27:22.724
It's happening again.

435
00:27:22.807 --> 00:27:24.643
[unsettling music playing]

436
00:27:24.726 --> 00:27:26.645
I think Father is

437
00:27:28.229 --> 00:27:29.856
becoming the pond spirit.

438
00:27:29.939 --> 00:27:31.733
I believe he is turning into it.

439
00:27:32.942 --> 00:27:34.819
The pond spirit. you say?

440
00:27:34.903 --> 00:27:37.656
The one who killed his brothers
30 years ago wasâ€¦

441
00:27:39.491 --> 00:27:40.700
It was His Majesty.

442
00:27:41.534 --> 00:27:42.535
What are youâ€¦

443
00:27:45.121 --> 00:27:47.248
-What are you trying to say. child?
-And now. once moreâ€¦

444
00:27:48.124 --> 00:27:50.085
It appears he'll do the same thing.

445
00:27:51.211 --> 00:27:54.297
He had Iksang's son summoned here
to the palace and poisoned him tonight.

446
00:27:56.758 --> 00:27:57.801
[scoffs]

447
00:27:59.135 --> 00:28:00.053
That cannot be.

448
00:28:00.136 --> 00:28:03.264
A lotus-patterned confectionery box
was found in the Prince's chambers.

449
00:28:03.348 --> 00:28:04.933
My mother received it as well.

450
00:28:06.768 --> 00:28:09.688
She died after eating the contents
of one just like that.

451
00:28:10.730 --> 00:28:12.565
-That cannot be.
-It's true.

452
00:28:13.650 --> 00:28:15.068
Grandmother. please.

453
00:28:15.151 --> 00:28:17.821
You also noticed something amiss
about Father. did you not?

454
00:28:17.904 --> 00:28:20.073
If you know anything. please say it.

455
00:28:20.156 --> 00:28:21.991
He must be stopped.
no matter what he does.

456
00:28:22.075 --> 00:28:23.618
And if there's no other way.

457
00:28:24.703 --> 00:28:26.955
then he must
relinquish the throne on his own.

458
00:28:29.040 --> 00:28:30.917
[breathing shakily]

459
00:28:36.548 --> 00:28:37.716
[Sukbin sobs]

460
00:28:43.179 --> 00:28:45.181
[sobbing continues]

461
00:28:46.766 --> 00:28:48.268
I do apologize.

462
00:28:49.227 --> 00:28:50.353
[Gu-cheon] <i>Disappeared?</i>

463
00:28:50.437 --> 00:28:51.521
[Ji-yul] Yes!

464
00:28:51.604 --> 00:28:53.690
I was certain she would be here.

465
00:28:53.773 --> 00:28:55.567
Oh. then where'd she go?

466
00:28:56.860 --> 00:28:58.903
Wait. just tell me what happened.

467
00:28:58.987 --> 00:29:00.989
[pensive ethereal music playing]

468
00:29:03.742 --> 00:29:05.952
When she heard from Lady Jang.

469
00:29:06.035 --> 00:29:09.205
who recently found
that Prince Inha had collapsed.

470
00:29:09.289 --> 00:29:13.084
she suddenly started to push people away
and walked off somewhere alone.

471
00:29:13.168 --> 00:29:16.129
They say the Princess's face. it was pale.

472
00:29:16.212 --> 00:29:19.299
She didn't look like herself at all.
like her spirit had fled.

473
00:29:19.382 --> 00:29:21.384
[percussive pensive music playing]

474
00:29:23.928 --> 00:29:26.389
The Princess's heart has fallen apart.

475
00:29:27.891 --> 00:29:30.268
[Ji-yul] Do you know where
the Princess is now?

476
00:29:31.394 --> 00:29:32.270
[Gu-cheon] <i>I do.</i>

477
00:29:32.771 --> 00:29:35.315
<i>A place where</i>
<i>there is someone she can rely on.</i>

478
00:29:39.694 --> 00:29:42.530
But that man. Gu-cheon. does heâ€¦

479
00:29:43.573 --> 00:29:45.617
does he know anything about this yet?

480
00:29:48.203 --> 00:29:49.829
Not about this.

481
00:29:50.455 --> 00:29:52.707
Only I. who can hear the voices.

482
00:29:54.125 --> 00:29:55.543
know what's happening.

483
00:29:58.004 --> 00:29:59.255
[slurps]

484
00:30:00.840 --> 00:30:02.091
Don't lie to me.

485
00:30:02.175 --> 00:30:04.302
[intriguing music playing]

486
00:30:07.680 --> 00:30:09.015
Sorry?

487
00:30:11.226 --> 00:30:12.435
[woman] <i>Saeng-gang.</i>

488
00:30:12.519 --> 00:30:14.062
[distant hissing]

489
00:30:14.145 --> 00:30:15.772
[distant spectral screams]

490
00:30:17.315 --> 00:30:18.316
[Saeng-gang] Mother?

491
00:30:20.026 --> 00:30:20.985
[gasps]

492
00:30:28.701 --> 00:30:31.454
[breathing shakily]

493
00:30:42.549 --> 00:30:43.967
This is a spell.

494
00:30:45.009 --> 00:30:47.637
[woman] <i>You must not remain</i>
<i>at that person's side.</i>

495
00:30:47.720 --> 00:30:48.763
[gasps]

496
00:30:53.142 --> 00:30:55.186
[woman] <i>I know you are the pond spirit.</i>

497
00:30:55.270 --> 00:30:57.021
<i>I know you are the pond spirit.</i>

498
00:30:57.105 --> 00:30:59.399
<i>It will all be revealed sooner or later.</i>

499
00:30:59.482 --> 00:31:03.278
[Sukbin chuckles] Seems your mother
is outside the chamber.

500
00:31:03.361 --> 00:31:05.530
How long will she
keep following me around?

501
00:31:05.613 --> 00:31:07.615
This is why I never wanted to come here.

502
00:31:07.699 --> 00:31:09.701
[tense percussive music playing]

503
00:31:11.786 --> 00:31:15.623
Soâ€¦ might she have other spirits with her?

504
00:31:17.458 --> 00:31:18.543
[woman] <i>Saeng-gang.</i>

505
00:31:19.752 --> 00:31:22.005
<i>You must not remain at that person's side.</i>

506
00:31:22.839 --> 00:31:24.465
<i>You must not remain at that person's side.</i>

507
00:31:24.549 --> 00:31:26.259
<i>You must not remain at that person's side.</i>

508
00:31:26.342 --> 00:31:28.970
<i>You must not remain at that person's side.</i>
<i>You must not remainâ€¦</i>

